


{"id":2272,"date":"2016-04-21T17:38:27","date_gmt":"2016-04-21T16:38:27","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/?page_id=2272"},"modified":"2025-05-01T23:21:32","modified_gmt":"2025-05-01T22:21:32","slug":"autoservis","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/autoservis\/","title":{"rendered":"Autoservis"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span12  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"row product-detail margin-bottom-45\">\n<div class=\"span6 \"><h2><strong>Zna\u010dkov\u00fd servis Volkswagen, Audi, Seat\/Cupra, \u0160koda, Volkswagen - u\u017eitkov\u00e9 vozy<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Zam\u011b\u0159ujeme se p\u0159ev\u00e1\u017en\u011b na servis voz\u016f koncernu <strong>Volkswagen AG<\/strong>. D\u00edky tomu zn\u00e1me v\u0161echny typy automobil\u016f do posledn\u00edho \u0161roubku. Ka\u017ed\u00e1 zna\u010dka m\u00e1 sv\u00e1 specifika, proto v\u00fdhradn\u011b pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1me origin\u00e1ln\u00ed d\u00edly, p\u0159\u00edstroje a za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed a\u00a0dodr\u017eujeme p\u0159\u00edsn\u00e9 kvalitativn\u00ed standardy\u00a0 p\u0159edepsan\u00e9 koncernem<strong>\u00a0Volkswagen AG<\/strong>. Sv\u011b\u0159te servis sv\u00e9ho auta do rukou specialist\u016f.<\/p>\n<p>P\u0159edch\u00e1zejte slo\u017eit\u00fdm oprav\u00e1m a zbyte\u010dn\u00fdm v\u00fddaj\u016fm pravidelnou prohl\u00eddkou va\u0161eho vozu.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Servisn\u00ed prohl\u00eddky<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>V r\u00e1mci pravideln\u00fdch servisn\u00edch prohl\u00eddek, jejich\u017e intervaly stanovuje v\u00fdrobce vozidla, dost\u00e1v\u00e1 v\u00e1\u0161 v\u016fz takovou p\u00e9\u010di, aby v maxim\u00e1ln\u00ed m\u00ed\u0159e eliminoval p\u0159\u00edpadn\u00e9 z\u00e1vady vznikl\u00e9 provozem vozidla. Dodr\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed t\u011bchto interval\u016f by m\u011blo b\u00fdt p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm v z\u00e1jmu u\u017eivatele vozidla. Jsme schopni prov\u00e1d\u011bt pravideln\u00e9 servisn\u00ed prohl\u00eddky v\u010detn\u011b v\u0161ech ostatn\u00edch oprav na v\u0161ech typech\u00a0 vozidel <strong>Volkswagen\u00a0AG<\/strong>. Zajist\u00edme pro v\u00e1s origin\u00e1ln\u00ed n\u00e1hradn\u00ed d\u00edly a vybereme nejvhodn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed n\u00e1pl\u0148 motorov\u00e9ho oleje. Samoz\u0159ejmost\u00ed je zaps\u00e1n\u00ed servisn\u00ed prohl\u00eddky do elektronick\u00e9 servisn\u00ed kn\u00ed\u017eky.<\/p><\/div>\n<div class=\"span6 \"><div class=\"motopress-image-obj motopress-text-align-left\"><img src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/autoservis-pro-firmy-01.jpg\" title=\"autoservis-pro-firmy-01\" alt=\"autoservis-pro-firmy-01\" class=\"motopress-image-obj-basic mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right mpce-dsbl-margin-top mpce-dsbl-margin-bottom\" \/><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><!-- .row (end) -->\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mp-row-fluid motopress-row mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"motopress-clmn mp-span12  mpce-dsbl-margin-left mpce-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"content_box call-to-action-row \"> <div class=\"row \"> <div class=\"span12 \"><p>Pro autoservis v <strong>Praze a okol\u00ed<\/strong> volejte +420 605 399 448, +420 608 313 437<br \/>\n(Po-P\u00e1 od 9 do 18 hod.)<\/p><\/div> <\/div><!-- .row (end) --> <div class=\"clear\"><\/div><\/div><!-- .content_box (end) -->\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<section class=\"parallax-box image-parallax-box no-margin\" ><div class=\"parallax-content\">\n<div class=\"row \">\n<div class=\"span12 \"><div class=\"service-box style_6\"><div class=\"service-box_body\"><h2 class=\"title\">V\u011bnujte pozornost<\/h2><h5 class=\"sub-title\">sv\u00e9mu vozu<\/h5><div class=\"service-box_txt\">Chcete v r\u00e1mci p\u0159\u00edpravy STK vyu\u017e\u00edt i dal\u0161\u00ed slu\u017eby? P\u0159ezujeme pneumatiky, dopln\u00edme klimatizaci nebo provedeme diagnostiku. A to v\u0161echno v r\u00e1mci jedn\u00e9 n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvy.<\/div><div class=\"btn-align\"><a href=\"\/dalsi-sluzby\/\" title=\"Zjistit v\u00edce\" class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" target=\"_self\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- \/Service Box --><\/div>\n<\/div><!-- .row (end) -->\n<div class=\"clear\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"parallax-bg\" data-parallax-type=\"image\" data-img-url=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/parallax-01.jpg\" data-speed=\"normal\" data-invert=\"false\" ><\/div><\/section>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-fullwidth.php","meta":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v17.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Servis Volkswagen, Audi, Seat\/Cupra, \u0160koda, Volkswagen - u\u017eitkov\u00e9 vozy | J&amp;S servis<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"P\u0159edch\u00e1zejte slo\u017eit\u00fdm oprav\u00e1m pravideln\u00fdmi kontrolami v autoservisu. Vyu\u017eijte zna\u010dkov\u00e9 p\u00e9\u010de o sv\u016fj v\u016fz s origin\u00e1ln\u00edmi d\u00edly a n\u00e1stroji zna\u010dky Volkswagen .\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/jasservis.cz\/autoservis\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"cs_CZ\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Servis Volkswagen, Audi, Seat\/Cupra, \u0160koda, Volkswagen - u\u017eitkov\u00e9 vozy | J&amp;S servis\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"P\u0159edch\u00e1zejte slo\u017eit\u00fdm oprav\u00e1m pravideln\u00fdmi kontrolami v autoservisu. Vyu\u017eijte zna\u010dkov\u00e9 p\u00e9\u010de o sv\u016fj v\u016fz s origin\u00e1ln\u00edmi d\u00edly a n\u00e1stroji zn